# Root build context — used ONLY by the ingester image build
# (docker-compose.yml: ingester.build.context = ".", dockerfile = ingester/Dockerfile).
#
# Why a root context: the ingester depends on the sibling `halley-canonical`
# crate via a path dependency (`../halley-canonical`, see ingester/Cargo.toml
# and D22/D54). A `./ingester` context cannot see that sibling, so the build is
# rooted here and we allow ONLY the two crates the ingester needs.
#
# Dashboard and worker keep their own subdir contexts (./dashboard, ./worker)
# and are unaffected by this file.

# Ignore everything by default, then re-include only the ingester + its crate dep.
*
!ingester
!halley-canonical

# Drop build artifacts and noise from the re-included trees.
ingester/target
halley-canonical/target
**/.DS_Store
